org.eclipse.dataset

Interface ILazyWriteableDataset

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDynamicDataset, ILazyDataset, IMetadataProvider, INameable, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LazyWriteableDataset

    public interface ILazyWriteableDataset
extends IDynamicDataset
    This sub-interface adds the ability to write to a lazy dataset slice-by-slice
